text: Cleidogonidae is a family of millipedes in the order Chordeumatida. There are about 6 genera and at least 160 described species in Cleidogonidae. ==Genera== * Cabraca Shear, 1982 * Cleidogona Cook, 1895 * Dybasia Loomis, 1964 * Pseudotremia Cope, 1869 * Solaenogona Hoffman, 1950 * Tiganogona Chamberlin, 1928 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Chordeumatida Category:Millipede families
